<questionnaire id="81259">
  <title>2014 State of Drupal DevOps</title>
  <investigator/>
  <dataCollector/>
  <questionnaireInfo>
    <position>before</position>
    <text>&lt;p&gt;&#13;
	Two years ago Kris Buytaert presented a survey to the Drupal community in order to gauge the state of DevOps in Drupal. You can see the slides from this presentation at http://www.slideshare.net/KrisBuytaert/drupal-and-devops-the-survey-results.  We have resurrected the essence of his original questionaire and will be presenting this data at Drupalcon Austin in https://austin2014.drupal.org/session/state-drupal-devops&lt;/p&gt;&#13;
&lt;p&gt;&#13;
	 &lt;/p&gt;&#13;
&lt;p&gt;&#13;
	Much like the Agile movements, the definition of DevOps changes between people and organizations.  The only way for us, as a community, to benefit from devops is to understand and share that knowledge.   We are interested in hearing from you if you have ever worked to deliver a Drupal site from a technical, or non-technical perspective.&lt;/p&gt;&#13;
&lt;p&gt;&#13;
	 &lt;/p&gt;&#13;
&lt;p&gt;&#13;
	In exhange for your time, I will be giving away a new 16g wifi iPad mini with Retina Display to a randomly chosen winner.  In order to qualify for the iPad you must fill out 100% of the survey questions.  The winner will be announced on stage at Drupalcon Austin during the presentation.&lt;/p&gt;&#13;
&lt;p&gt;&#13;
	 &lt;/p&gt;&#13;
&lt;p&gt;&#13;
	Your contact information will only be used to send you the ipad if you win or to send you the survey results if you select that checkbox. If at any time, you would like your results completely removed from the survey, simply let me know.  If you would like to discuss any of this before submitting, you can receive assistance at https://groups.drupal.org/devops&lt;/p&gt;&#13;
&lt;p&gt;&#13;
	 &lt;/p&gt;&#13;
&lt;p&gt;&#13;
	This survey will expire on May.05.2014 00:00&lt;/p&gt;</text>
    <administration>self</administration>
  </questionnaireInfo>
  <questionnaireInfo>
    <position>after</position>
    <text>Thanks for participating in our survey, we'll share the results soon on https://groups.drupal.org/devops</text>
    <administration>self</administration>
  </questionnaireInfo>
